<pre><code>
    let sty = document.createElement('style');
    sty.textContent = `
    body{margin:0!important;padding:0!important;}
    /*img{position:absolute;left:0!important;top:0!important;}*/
    #mousePosition{color:red!important;position:absolute!important;text-shadow:1px 0 1px cyan!important;}
    #verticalLine{width:0!important;border-left:1px solid red!important;line-height:100!important;position:fixed!important;}
    #horizontalLine{width:100%!important;border-top:1px solid red!important;position:absolute!important;}
    `;

    document.body.appendChild(sty);
    let pos = document.createElement('span');
    pos.id='mousePosition';
    document.body.appendChild(pos);

    let verticalLine = document.createElement('div');
    verticalLine.id = 'verticalLine';
    verticalLine.innerHTML = '&nbsp;';
    document.body.appendChild(verticalLine);

    let horizontalLine = document.createElement('div');
    horizontalLine.id = 'horizontalLine';
    horizontalLine.innerHTML = '&nbsp;';
    document.body.appendChild(horizontalLine);

    document.addEventListener('mousemove', (evt)=>{
      let tar = document.getElementById('mousePosition');
      tar.textContent = 'X:'+evt.pageX+' Y:'+evt.pageY;
      tar.style.left = evt.pageX+20+'px';
      tar.style.top = evt.pageY+'px';

      verticalLine.style.left = evt.pageX + 'px';
      horizontalLine.style.top = evt.pageY + 'px';
    }, false);
</code></pre>
